data.enText: She was only a few pounds overweight.

data.chText: 超过限制重量的；过重的

tr: usually describes a large person who is fat but has a large frame to carry it

value.def: Someone who is overweight weighs more than is considered healthy or attractive.

example.ex: Being even moderately overweight increases your risk of developing high blood pressure.
example.tran: 即使是轻度超重也会增加患高血压的风险。
